rate with a $3,000 down payment

198
00:07:35,850 --> 00:07:38,520
and a 1,000 pound trade-in of your old car

199
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:43,520
you'll be paying $382.02
a month for 60 months.

200
00:07:44,010 --> 00:07:45,660
However, you'll also have to consider

201
00:07:45,660 --> 00:07:47,730
the depreciation of the vehicle.

202
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:50,850
A new car loses around 22% of its value

203
00:07:50,850 --> 00:07:54,660
in the first year and
around 55% over five years.

204
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:56,460
This means that halfway through your loan,

205
00:07:56,460 --> 00:07:59,040
